  • Method Details

    • hookNativeWidget

      protected void hookNativeWidget(Object widget)
      Description copied from class: AbstractCSSEngine
      Called when an element context is created for a native widget and registered with this engine. Subclasses should override and install a listener on the widget that will call AbstractCSSEngine.handleWidgetDisposed(Object) when the widget is disposed.

      The default implementation of this method does nothing.

      Overrides:
      hookNativeWidget in class AbstractCSSEngine
      Parameters:
      widget - the native widget to hook
